---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Fusion Victoria | Reclaim Our State. They Stole It. We're Taking It Back."
  description="Contesting Victoria's 2026 state election. 50,000 public homes. Melton Line in 4 years. End infrastructure waste. Real solutions for Melbourne's West and all of Victoria."
>
  <Header />
  
  <!-- ALERT BAR -->
  <div class="alert-bar">
    üó≥Ô∏è Contesting Victoria's 2026 State Election | <a href="#electorates">Find your electorate</a>
  </div>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <Hero 
    eyebrow="Victoria 2026"
    title="RECLAIM OUR STATE"
    subtitle="They wasted billions. We'll build what you need."
    stats={heroStats}
    showCTA={true}
  />

  <!-- THE THEFT - Victoria Specific -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #c926f2;">THE VICTORIAN THEFT</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">
          They've been in power for decades. Both major parties. Here's what 
          they've stolen from you while taking donations from developers, 
          fossil fuel companies, and private hospitals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="theft-grid">
        {theftCards.map(card => (
          <div class="theft-card">
            <img src={card.image} alt={card.category} class="theft-card-image" />
            <div class="theft-card-content">
              <div class="theft-card-category">{card.category}</div>
              <h3>{card.amount}</h3>
              <p class="theft-card-description">{card.description}</p>
              <div class="theft-card-impact">
                <strong>Your Impact:</strong>
                <p>{card.impact}</p>
              </div>
              <a href={card.link}>{card.linkText} ‚Üí</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ELECTORATES -->
  <section id="electorates" class="bg-light-grey py-20 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4" style="color: #c926f2;">OUR CANDIDATES</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">
          Local people with real plans to fix the failures in their communities. 
          Not career politicians. Not beholden to donors.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="electorate-grid">
        {electorates.map(electorate => (
          <div class="electorate-card">
            <h3>{electorate.name}</h3>
            <span class="candidate-name">{electorate.candidate}</span>
            <p>{electorate.description}</p>
            <ul class="electorate-priorities">
              {electorate.priorities.map(priority => (
                <li set:html={priority} />
              ))}
            </ul>
            <a href={electorate.link}>Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
          <strong>Not in one of these electorates?</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We're building campaigns across Victoria. Help us bring Fusion to your area.
        </p>
        <a href="/get-involved" class="btn btn-primary">VOLUNTEER IN YOUR AREA</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MANIFESTO HIGHLIGHT -->
  <section class="bg-magenta-gradient text-white py-20 px-8 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6">THE VICTORIA MANIFESTO</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8">
        Our complete plan to fix Victoria's broken systems. Every policy 
        costed. Every claim sourced. Every promise tracked.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 my-12">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-6 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-5xl font-black block mb-2" style="color: #5effd8;">50,000</span>
          <span class="text-sm">Public homes over 4 years</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-6 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-5xl font-black block mb-2" style="color: #5effd8;">$2.8B</span>
          <span class="text-sm">Infrastructure waste cut per year</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-6 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-5xl font-black block mb-2" style="color: #5effd8;">4</span>
          <span class="text-sm">New public hospitals</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-6 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-5xl font-black block mb-2" style="color: #5effd8;">2030</span>
          <span class="text-sm">100% renewable electricity</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/manifesto" class="btn btn-secondary">READ FULL MANIFESTO</a>
        <a href="/policies" class="btn btn-secondary">SEE THE COSTINGS</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TAKE ACTION -->
  <section class="bg-magenta-gradient text-white py-20 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-center mb-6">JOIN THE FIGHT</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Victoria won't fix itself. The major parties have had decades 
        and delivered failure. Real change requires a movement of working 
        people who've had enough.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-lg p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üö™</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">VOLUNTEER</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Door knock in your electorate. Phone bank. Help at events. 
            Even a few hours makes a difference. This is how we win.
          </p>
          <a href="/get-involved" class="btn btn-primary">SIGN UP NOW</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-lg p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üí∞</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">DONATE</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            We don't take corporate money. Every dollar comes from 
            people like you, $20-$50 at a time. That's why we answer 
            to you.
          </p>
          <a href="/get-involved#donate" class="btn btn-secondary">CONTRIBUTE</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-lg p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üì¢</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">SPREAD THE WORD</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Share our policies. Print our fact sheets. Talk to your 
            neighbors. When people complain, tell them there's a 
            real alternative.
          </p>
          <a href="/manifesto" class="btn btn-secondary">GET MATERIALS</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
